    "date": "2022-04-01T13:41:33Z",
    "text": "Mental Health Research Accelerator Act of 2022\n\nThis bill allows a tax credit through 2031 for 25% of expenses for translational research regarding neurodegenerative diseases and psychiatric conditions. The credit amount is subject to limitations, including an aggregate national limitation of $1 billion in 2022, $2 billion in 2023-2027, and $1 billion in 2028."
